quran[7{c,v,t}:
7,31,ae nabi aadam! har namaz ke waqt apne tain muzayyankiya karo aur khao aur پیؤ aur be ja nah urrao ke khuda be ja urane walon ko dost nahi rakhta
7,32,pucho to ke jo zeenat ( vaaraysh ) aur khanay ( peenay ) ki pakeeza cheezein khuda ne apne bundon ke liye peda ki hain un ko haraam kis nekiya hai? keh do ke yeh cheezein duniya ki zindagi mein imaan walon ke liye hain aur qayamat ke din khaas un hi ka hissa hon gi. isi terhan khuda apni ayatain samajhney walon ke liye khol khol kar bayan farmata hai
7,33,keh do ke mere perwar-digaar ne to be hiyai ki baton ko zahir hon ya posheeda aur gunah ko aur na-haq zayad-ti karne ko haraamkiya hai. aur is ko bhi ke tum kisi ko khuda ka shareek banaao jis ki is ne koi sanad nazil nahi ki aur is ko bhi ke khuda ke baray mein aisi baatein kaho jin ka tumhe kuch ilm nahi
7,34,aur har aik firqay ke liye ( mout ka ) aik waqt muqarrar hai. jab woh aa jata hai to nah to aik gharri der kar saktay hain nah jaldi
7,35,ae nabi aadam! ( hum tum ko yeh nasiyaat hamesha karte rahay hain ke ) jab hamaray paighambar tumahray paas aaya karen aur hamari ayatain tum ko sunaya karen ( to un par imaan laya karo ) ke jo shakhs ( un par imaan laa kar khuda se ) darta rahay ga aur apni haalat durust rakhay ga to aisay logon ko nah kuch khauf hoga aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge
7,36,aur jinhon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya aur un se sartabi ki wohi dozakhi hain ke hamesha is mein ( jaltay ) rahen ge
7,37,to is se ziyada zalim kon hai jo khuda par jhoot bandhay ya is ki ayaton ko jhutlaye. un ko un ke naseeb ka likha milta hi rahay ga yahan taq ke jab un ke paas hamaray beje hue ( farishtay ) jaan nikaalte ayen ge to kahin ge ke jin ko tum khuda ke siwa puraka karte they woh ( ab ) kahan hain? woh kahin ge ( maloom nahi ) ke woh hum se ( kahan ) gayab hogaye aur iqraar karen ge ke be shak woh kafir they
